name: Lisa Lashes
description:
'''Lisa Dawn Rose-Wyatt''' (born  on 23 April 1971 in [[Coventry]], England), known by her stage name '''Lisa Lashes''', is an English [[electronic dance music]] [[Disc jockey|DJ]] and producer known for mixing numerous [[Euphoria (compilations)|''Euphoria'']] albums and her Lashed dance music events.
She has headlined European and international music festivals such as [[Global Gathering]], [[Creamfields]], [[Nocturnal Wonderland]] and [[Dance Valley]], UK events such as [[Godskitchen]], [[Gatecrasher]], Inside Out and Planet Love. She has toured China, Canada, the US, Russia, Australia and [[New Zealand]].
